If you have an error c2244 , change



In itkstructuretensorimagefilter.h 

  typedef typename          TensorImageType::Pointer       TensorImagePointer;
  typedef typename          GradientImageType::Pointer     GradientImagePointer;

to

  typedef typename          TOutputImage::Pointer       TensorImagePointer;
  typedef typename          TOutputImage2::Pointer     GradientImagePointer;


and it works...
